'''Kehillat Israel''' is a [[Reconstructionist Judaism|reconstructionist congregation]] in [[Pacific Palisades, Los Angeles]].<ref name=KI>{{Cite web|last= |first= |authorlink= |title=Kehillat Israel |publisher=Kehillat Israel|date= |url=https://www.ourki.org/ |accessdate=October 31, 2018}}</ref> They are one of two reconstructionist synagogues in greater Los Angeles (the other being the Malibu Jewish Center and Synagogue).<ref name=JJTorek>{{Cite web|last=Torek |first=Ryan |authorlink= |title=Reconstructionist Group Votes to Change Its Name |publisher=[[The Jewish Journal of Greater Los Angeles|Jewish Journal]]|date=February 7, 2018 |url=http://jewishjournal.com/news/los_angeles/230564/reconstructionist-group-votes-change-name/|accessdate=October 31, 2018}}</ref> Their senior rabbi is Amy Bernstein.<ref name=JJTorek />
==History== Prominent current and former members include: *[[Lloyd Braun]], former Chairman of the [[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]] Entertainment Group<ref>{{Cite web|last= |first= |authorlink= |title=kiQuarterly |publisher=Kehillat Israel|date=December 2017 |url=https://images.shulcloud.com/1239/uploads/Documents/KIQuarterlyDec17Feb18Final1114-1.pdf |accessdate=}}</ref> *[[Alden Ehrenreich]], actor<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kehillatisrael.org/_downloader.php?file_id=191|title=Kvell Corner|website=Kehillat Israel Reconstructionist Congregation|accessdate=May 27, 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110726214729/http://kehillatisrael.org/_downloader.php?file_id=191|archivedate=July 26, 2011}}</ref> *[[Jon Feltheimer]], CEO of [[Lions Gate Entertainment]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ourki.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/KI-news_Dec2011.pdf|date=Dec 2011|title=kinews ''Volume 61, Issue 4''|publisher=Kehillat Israel|page=7}}</ref> *[[Ellie Kanner]], director<ref>[http://ourki.org/Websites/kehillatisraeltest/files/Content/2039479/KINewsMay-Aug.2012_web.pdf Kehillat Israel Reconstructionist Congregation of Pacific Palisades Bulletin] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045443/http://ourki.org/Websites/kehillatisraeltest/files/Content/2039479/KINewsMay-Aug.2012_web.pdf |date=2016-03-04 }} MAY-AUGUST 2012 | Iyar/AV 5772 - Volume 61 | Issue 9</ref> *[[John Whitesell]], director<ref>[http://ourki.org/commitment-to-community-list/ Kehillat Israel: "COMMITMENT TO COMMUNITY"] retrieved December 5, 2016</ref>
