'''Théophane Matthew Thannickunnel''' (September 23, 1928 &ndash; November 18, 2016) was a [[Roman Catholic]] bishop.

Ordained to the priesthood in 1959, Thannickunnel served as the bishop of the [[Roman Catholic Diocese of Jabalpur]], [[India]] from 1975 to 2001.<ref>[http://www.gcatholic.org/dioceses/diocese/jaba0.htm Diocese of Jabapur]</ref>

